I've been able to do some weird shit.

1140
01:18:04,130 --> 01:18:05,420
躲在我身后
Stay behind me.

1141
01:18:05,700 --> 01:18:07,330
我还能去哪儿
Where else am I gonna go?

1142
01:18:07,350 --> 01:18:08,680
带我们离开这里
Get us out of here!

1143
01:18:09,290 --> 01:18:10,860
知道什么时候该等待
Know when to wait.

1144
01:18:11,560 --> 01:18:13,640
现在没那么好笑了  是吧
Not so fucking funny now, eh?

1145
01:18:14,070 --> 01:18:17,700
皇后陛下  恢复我的力量  让我干掉他
My Queen, restore me now! Let me finish him!

1146
01:18:17,710 --> 01:18:19,300
现在还不行
Not just yet.

1147
01:18:19,300 --> 01:18:21,040
