But you swore...

1148
01:18:21,290 --> 01:18:22,950
管好你的舌头  猪头
Mind your tongue, pig.

1149
01:18:22,950 --> 01:18:23,880
快走
Move it.

1150
01:18:25,100 --> 01:18:26,230
进去
Get in.

1151
