We do! But it's not gonna work, you know,

1162
01:19:07,120 --> 01:19:11,700
因为我是摩羯座  而你是他妈疯子座
'cause I'm a Capricorn and you're fucking nuts!

1163
01:19:13,170 --> 01:19:16,480
你的体内沉睡着恶魔  我会唤醒它
A demon sleeps inside you, and I will waken it.

1164
01:19:16,480 --> 01:19:19,430
地狱男爵  地狱男爵
Hellboy! Hellboy!

1165
01:19:22,200 --> 01:19:24,870
