Where?

1178
01:19:59,070 --> 01:20:01,140
你不会真要听她的吧
You're not seriously gonna listen to her!

1179
01:20:01,280 --> 01:20:03,090
她可能会把我们引入陷阱
She could be leading us straight into a trap!

1180
01:20:04,190 --> 01:20:05,510
你可以救你的朋友
You can save your friend.

1181
01:20:09,910 --> 01:20:11,700
我们别无选择
We don't have a choice.

1182
01:20:11,700 --> 01:20:13,100
去黑鳍山
Go to Black Fin.

1183
01:20:14,330 --> 01:20:15,460
在悬崖顶上
High atop the cliffs

1184
01:20:15,460 --> 01:20:17,790
岩石中隐藏着一条古老的牧羊道
there's an old goat path hidden in the rocks.

1185
01:20:17,790 --> 01:20:19,530
这条路充满危险
The way is treacherous,

1186
01:20:19,630 --> 01:20:22,610
但你必须沿着它走到尽头
but you must follow it until you can go no further.

1187
01:20:23,460 --> 01:20:27,130
在那  你会在山洞中找到通往地球内部的通道
There, you'll find a passage into the bowels of the Earth, in a cave.

1188
01:20:27,130 --> 01:20:28,340
这边  戴米奥
This way, Daimio.

1189
01:20:28,340 --> 01:20:29,890
你要找的人就在那里
The one you seek is there.

1190
01:20:29,890 --> 01:20:31,370
智者梅林
Merlin the Wise.

1191
01:20:31,850 --> 01:20:34,810
国王的巫师  愚者的国王
Wizard to kings, and king of fools.

1192
01:20:34,810 --> 01:20:37,600
