Cursed to live forever buried in a hole

1193
01:20:37,600 --> 01:20:39,880
而被诅咒永远活埋在洞里
for allowing Arthur to betray the truce.

1194
01:20:50,320 --> 01:20:52,700
你终于要带走我的灵魂了吗
Have you finally come to claim my soul?

1195
01:20:52,700 --> 01:20:54,190
我不是死神
That's the other guy.

1196
01:20:55,750 --> 01:20:58,500
快点  我的朋友中毒了
Come on! My friend's been poisoned,

1197
01:20:58,500 --> 01:21:00,650
