我见过这个  这是妮缪干的
I have seen this before. This is Nimue's work.

1199
01:21:09,430 --> 01:21:11,390
你不能小瞧这个女巫
You cannot underestimate this witch.

1200
01:21:11,390 --> 01:21:13,120
她是邪恶的化身
She is evil incarnate.

1201
01:21:13,720 --> 01:21:15,520
如果我们迅速行动  还有机会
There's still a chance if we act quickly.

1202
01:21:15,520 --> 01:21:17,790
