Welcome back.

1209
01:21:58,020 --> 01:21:59,310
新来的是谁
Who's the new guy?

1210
01:21:59,310 --> 01:22:01,460
我说了你肯定不信
You wouldn't believe me if I told you.

1211
01:22:04,610 --> 01:22:05,940
