are there still tales of King Arthur in your time?

1218
01:22:25,250 --> 01:22:27,440
他是怎样从石头中拔出剑来
How he drew the sword from the stone?

1219
01:22:27,440 --> 01:22:29,010
是的  还有电影
Yeah. Movies, too.

1220
01:22:29,010 --> 01:22:31,170
