Son of Arthur, last of the royal lineage.

1241
01:23:37,280 --> 01:23:38,770
他的血脉
Blood of his blood.

1242
01:23:38,950 --> 01:23:41,100
注定要成为人类之王
Destined to be king of man.

1243
01:23:45,040 --> 01:23:46,620
所以我知道你是
Which is why I know you are

1244
01:23:46,630 --> 01:23:49,400
